# modpot active-probe scope file (AUTHORIZED USE ONLY).
# One target per line as HOST[:PORT]; default port is 502.
# Lines starting with # are ignored. Only list devices you OWN or are
# explicitly contracted to assess — out-of-scope targets are never probed.
#
# Example (replace with your authorized devices):
# 10.0.0.5:502
# 10.0.0.6
# 127.0.0.1:5020
